    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26062915_4_668-708",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "668-708",
      "markText": "这使我想起了他在风烛残年之时，经常说的一句话，说话之时，双眸生辉：“我还没死！”",
      "totalCount": 1224,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26062915&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=668&rangeEnd=708",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cd732d70718db043cd73bb3?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=668&rangeEnd=708"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26062915_9_690-720",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "690-720",
      "markText": "世上的事儿就这样：你没白没黑地干，却什么也得不到，天天如此。",
      "totalCount": 1134,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26062915&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=690&rangeEnd=720",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cd732d70718db043cd73bb3?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=690&rangeEnd=720"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26062915_13_6173-6222",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "6173-6222",
      "markText": "“你要是知道，你正在和米特普拉斯特公司的首席化学家交谈，会觉得很有趣吧，他手下只有一个洗瓶子的！”",
      "totalCount": 1095,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26062915&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=6173&rangeEnd=6222",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cd732d70718db043cd73bb3?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=6173&rangeEnd=6222"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26062915_8_8428-8492",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "8428-8492",
      "markText": "我在上中学干的另外一件事儿，是发明问题和定理。我的意思是，如果我做无论什么数学的东西，我都会找到一些实际例子来说明它有什么用处。",
      "totalCount": 1088,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26062915&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=8428&rangeEnd=8492",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cd732d70718db043cd73bb3?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=8428&rangeEnd=8492"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26062915_8_1401-1523",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "1401-1523",
      "markText": "有天晚上，我妈妈和爸爸外出回来，蹑手蹑脚的没一点儿声音，怕吵着孩子啊，开了我房间的门，好拿开耳机。突然之间，那个巨大的铃儿震天价地响起来——乓乓乓乓乓！我大叫着从床上跳了下来：“管用啊！管用啊！”",
      "totalCount": 992,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26062915&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=1401&rangeEnd=1523",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cd732d70718db043cd73bb3?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=1401&rangeEnd=1523"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26062915_9_1966-1998",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "1966-1998",
      "markText": "世界真的是怎么样，和它瞧上去是怎么样，这两者之间，就有这个区别。",
      "totalCount": 924,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26062915&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=1966&rangeEnd=1998",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cd732d70718db043cd73bb3?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=1966&rangeEnd=1998"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26062915_16_3026-3080",
      "chapterUid": 16,
      "range": "3026-3080",
      "markText": "我因此发现催眠是一种非常有趣的体验。你一直在对自己说：“我能做那件事儿，但我不想做”——换句话说，你做不到。",
      "totalCount": 912,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26062915&chapterUid=16&rangeStart=3026&rangeEnd=3080",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cd732d70718db043cd73bb3?chapterUid=16&rangeStart=3026&rangeEnd=3080"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26062915_8_6938-6971",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "6938-6971",
      "markText": "因此，一个家伙花费了我20分钟，而另外五个家伙认为我是个超级天才。",
      "totalCount": 782,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26062915&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=6938&rangeEnd=6971",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cd732d70718db043cd73bb3?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=6938&rangeEnd=6971"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26062915_8_9817-9862",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "9817-9862",
      "markText": "我这才意识到，如果我要跟别人谈事情，我一定要用标准符号，因此我最后还是放弃了我自己的符号。",
      "totalCount": 774,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26062915&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=9817&rangeEnd=9862",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cd732d70718db043cd73bb3?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=9817&rangeEnd=9862"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26062915_8_10000-10047",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "10000-10047",
      "markText": "找到毛病在哪儿，还有琢磨出你该怎么修它，这整个的问题——对我而言，真是有趣，就跟难题一样有趣。",
